UMAP compatibility work
-----------------------

Some UMAP graph and optimizer details were studied against `uwot` so that
fastEmbedR can be compared fairly with `uwot::umap(..., fast_sgd = TRUE)`.
The installed `uwot` package reports License: GPL (>= 3). Any implementation
