RAPIDS/cuML and cuVS design references
--------------------------------------

The native GPU NN-descent roadmap studies RAPIDS cuML and cuVS, both
distributed under Apache-2.0:

  RAPIDS cuML
  Repository: https://github.com/rapidsai/cuml
  License: Apache-2.0

  RAPIDS cuVS
  Repository: https://github.com/rapidsai/cuvs
  License: Apache-2.0

The optional `nn(..., backend = "cuda_cuvs")`,
`nn(..., backend = "cuda_cuvs_bruteforce")`, and
`nn(..., backend = "cuda_cuvs_nndescent")` paths link to an external RAPIDS
cuVS installation only when it is available at package build time. No RAPIDS
